Single/multi-choice problem: Which of the following solutions is better for the following goal:
What toots do you need to build a mini coffin?

Options: A. You will need Miter Saw, Table Saw, Sander, Wood Clamps, Tape Measure, and a Pencil.; B. You will need Miter Saw, Table Saw, Sander, Wood Clamps, Tape Measure, and a highlighter.;

Review: This is one of my favorite films of all time. Al Pacino acting is at its best and the story is excellent. Too bad it didn't do to well in the 80's when it was first released because people didn't get a chance to experience this classic.
